{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocationVisible"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your app must specify a value for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"type":"text","text":" to satisfy the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"locationManager"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"showsUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","title":"showsUserLocation","roleHeading":"Instance Property","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/showsUserLocation":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user locat